Metric - RMSE¶

$$RMSE = \sqrt{\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^{n}(y_{i} - x_{i})^{2}}$$
In [256]:
models_list = [DecisionTree(), RandomForest(), GradientBoosting()]

models_grids = [
       
    {'max_depth' : range(3,30,3)},
   
    {'n_estimators' : range(50,300,10), 'max_depth' : [1,3,5]},

    {'n_estimators' : range(50,300,10), 'max_depth' : [1,3,5]}
    
              ]

lags = [1,2,3,4,5,6,7]
